### COMPLETE LOAN FLOW EXAMPLES

### 1. Create a Client
POST http://localhost:3000/client
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Maria da Silva",
  "dataNascimento": "1985-03-15",
  "cpf": "123.456.789-09",
  "rendaLiquidaMensal": 8000.00
}

### 2. Check Eligibility
POST http://localhost:3000/eligibility/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "{{CLIENT_ID_FROM_STEP_1}}",
  "requestedAmount": 30000,
  "purpose": "shopping",
  "firstPaymentDate": "2025-10-15"
}

### 3. Create Simulation (Generate Offers)
POST http://localhost:3000/simulation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "{{CLIENT_ID_FROM_STEP_1}}",
  "requestedAmount": 30000,
  "purpose": "shopping",
  "firstPaymentDate": "2025-10-15",
  "numberOfInstallments": 24
}

### 4. Create Contract (Accept an Offer)
POST http://localhost:3000/contract
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offerId": "{{OFFER_ID_FROM_STEP_3}}"
}

### 5. List Client Contracts
GET http://localhost:3000/contract/client/{{CLIENT_ID_FROM_STEP_1}}

